---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Eye Exam in Tijuana | Ópticas Jarmar Zona Río"
  description="Comprehensive eye exam in Tijuana with high-precision diagnostic equipment. Glaucoma detection, fundus exam and more. Ópticas Jarmar Zona Río."
  alternates={[
    { hreflang: "en", href: "https://jarmar.com/en/tijuana/eye-exam/" },
    { hreflang: "es", href: "https://jarmar.com/tijuana/estudio-de-la-vista/" },
    { hreflang: "x-default", href: "https://jarmar.com/tijuana/estudio-de-la-vista/" }
  ]}
>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #071A3E;
      --surface: #0D2B6B;
      --accent: #3A8FE0;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 100px 20px 80px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(58,143,224,0.2);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 6px 18px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      opacity: 0.85;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .btn-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-cta:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-2px); }

    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

    .section { padding: 72px 20px; }
    .section:nth-child(even) { background: #f7f9fc; }
    .section-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--bg);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-title span { color: var(--accent); }
    .section-sub {
      color: #4a5568;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .checklist {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .checklist li {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(58,143,224,0.25);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #2d3748;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .checklist li::before {
      content: "✓";
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 28px 22px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .card-icon { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }
    .card h4 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .card p { font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.85; line-height: 1.6; }

    .faq { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
    .faq-item {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(58,143,224,0.2);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 24px 28px;
    }
    .faq-item h4 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--bg);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .faq-item p { color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1rem; }

    .cta-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; opacity: 0.85; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 560px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

    .back-link {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-tag">Eye Health · Tijuana</span>
      <h1>Comprehensive Eye Exam<br>in <span>Tijuana</span></h1>
      <p>Full eye exam with high-precision diagnostic equipment. We detect glaucoma, fundus abnormalities, and more before they affect your quality of life.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+to+schedule+an+eye+exam+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Book my exam →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What does the <span>eye exam</span> include?</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Our eye exam goes beyond measuring your prescription. We use state-of-the-art equipment to give you a comprehensive view of your ocular health.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Visual acuity (near and far)</li>
        <li>Subjective and objective refraction</li>
        <li>Tonometry (glaucoma screening)</li>
        <li>Dilated fundus exam</li>
        <li>Binocular vision evaluation</li>
        <li>Ocular surface health</li>
        <li>Visual field assessment</li>
        <li>Slit-lamp eyelid and cornea exam</li>
        <li>Cataract and retinopathy screening</li>
        <li>Doctor's report and recommendations</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Who is the <span>eye exam</span> for?</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">We recommend an annual eye exam for the whole family. We have specialized protocols for every stage of life.</p>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <span class="card-icon">🧒</span>
          <h4>Children from age 3</h4>
          <p>Early detection of problems that affect school performance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="card-icon">👨</span>
          <h4>Young adults</h4>
          <p>Assessment of digital eye strain and frequent prescription changes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="card-icon">💊</span>
          <h4>Diabetics & hypertensive patients</h4>
          <p>Monitoring of retinopathy and vascular damage in the eyes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="card-icon">👴</span>
          <h4>Seniors</h4>
          <p>Glaucoma, cataract, and macular degeneration monitoring.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked <span>questions</span></h2>
      <div class="faq">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>How long does the exam take?</h4>
          <p>The full exam takes 30 to 45 minutes depending on the tests needed. If pupil dilation is included, it may extend to 60 minutes. We recommend coming with someone who can drive, as dilation can temporarily blur your vision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>Do I need an appointment?</h4>
          <p>Walk-ins are welcome, but we recommend booking via WhatsApp to ensure prompt attention and give the optometrist the time needed for your full evaluation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>How often should I get an eye exam?</h4>
          <p>Ideally once a year. If you have diabetes, glaucoma, or a family history of eye disease, every 6 months or as directed by your specialist is recommended.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>Do you accept patients from the US?</h4>
          <p>Yes! We welcome patients from San Diego, Chula Vista, and all of Southern California. Our clinic is bilingual and located in Zona Río, minutes from the border crossing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>When did you last have your eyes checked?</h2>
      <p>Book your eye exam at Ópticas Jarmar Tijuana today. Your vision health can't wait.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+to+schedule+an+eye+exam+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Book via WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a href="/en/tijuana/" class="back-link">← Back to Tijuana</a>
</BaseLayout>
